questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you require me to provide you my WordPress Login?
questionsAndAnswers.answer:
Yes, I will need your website WordPress login. If your WordPress not installed, then you need to provide me your Cpanel access, so that I can install WordPress first.
Thanks!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Will you work instead of Wordpress.
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will work with Weebly and WIX platforms. I will also develop and work on websites, not on any CMS using HTML5, CSS3, and Java Script (But contact me first).

questionsAndAnswers.question: What type of jobs you will not do?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I don't work on Adult websites and the websites against the Fiverr policies. Thanks!

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide customer support?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes, I will provide 1-month free customer support.
